---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTA from '../components/CTA.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="소개 | 데크센터"
  description="데크센터는 누구나 쉽게 프로페셔널한 데크를 설계할 수 있는 3D 시뮬레이터를 만듭니다. 복잡한 CAD 없이 드래그 앤 드롭으로 완벽한 데크를 디자인하세요."
>
  <div class="about-hero">
    <div class="about-hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="about-hero-content">
      <span class="eyebrow">About Us</span>
      <h1>누구나 프로처럼 설계하는 세상</h1>
      <p>복잡한 도구 없이, 내 손으로 완벽한 데크를 디자인하세요</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="about-container">
    <!-- 비전/미션 섹션 -->
    <section class="vision-section">
      <div class="vision-content">
        <div class="vision-item">
          <span class="vision-label">MISSION</span>
          <h2>"데크 설계의 문턱을<br/>낮춥니다"</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="vision-item">
          <span class="vision-label">VISION</span>
          <p class="vision-text">데크 설계의 새로운 기준</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
              <path d="M8 14s1.5 2 4 2 4-2 4-2"></path>
              <line x1="9" y1="9" x2="9.01" y2="9"></line>
              <line x1="15" y1="9" x2="15.01" y2="9"></line>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>쉬운 사용성</h3>
          <p>복잡한 CAD 프로그램 없이 누구나 5분 안에 데크 설계를 시작할 수 있습니다.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>정확한 설계</h3>
          <p>실제 시공 가능한 도면과 정확한 자재 리스트를 자동으로 생성합니다.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>신뢰할 수 있는 견적</h3>
          <p>실시간으로 계산되는 자재비로 예산 계획을 정확하게 세울 수 있습니다.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 스토리 섹션 -->
    <section class="story-section">
      <div class="story-content">
        <h2>왜 데크센터를 만들었나요?</h2>
        <p>
          데크를 설치하려면 전문가에게 의뢰하거나 복잡한 CAD 프로그램을 배워야 했습니다.
          간단한 마당 데크 하나를 설계하는데도 시간과 비용이 많이 들었죠.
        </p>
        <p>
          "왜 데크 설계는 이렇게 어려워야 할까?"
        </p>
        <p>
          이 질문에서 데크센터가 시작되었습니다. 우리는 누구나 드래그 앤 드롭만으로
          프로페셔널한 데크를 설계할 수 있는 도구를 만들고 있습니다.
          복잡한 것은 우리가 처리하고, 사용자는 창의적인 부분에만 집중할 수 있도록.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 통계 -->
    <section class="stats-section">
      <div class="stats-grid">
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-number">10,000+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">설계 완료</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-number">5,000+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">활성 사용자</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-number">100+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">자재 종류</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-number">4.9</span>
          <span class="stat-label">사용자 평점</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 타겟 사용자 -->
    <section class="users-section">
      <h2>이런 분들이 사용합니다</h2>
      <div class="users-grid">
        <div class="user-card">
          <div class="user-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"></path>
              <polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>DIY 개인</h3>
          <p>마당이나 옥상에 데크를 직접 설치하려는 개인 사용자</p>
        </div>
        <div class="user-card">
          <div class="user-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
              <path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>시공업체</h3>
          <p>고객에게 빠르게 시뮬레이션을 보여주고 견적을 제안하는 전문 업체</p>
        </div>
        <div class="user-card">
          <div class="user-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <polygon points="12 2 2 7 12 12 22 7 12 2"></polygon>
              <polyline points="2 17 12 22 22 17"></polyline>
              <polyline points="2 12 12 17 22 12"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>설계사무소</h3>
          <p>초기 설계 단계에서 데크 레이아웃을 빠르게 검토하는 전문가</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 로드맵 -->
    <section class="roadmap-section">
      <h2>로드맵</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">데크센터는 계속 발전하고 있습니다</p>
      <div class="roadmap">
        <div class="roadmap-item done">
          <div class="roadmap-status">완료</div>
          <h3>기본 3D 설계</h3>
          <p>드래그 앤 드롭 인터페이스, 기본 자재 라이브러리</p>
        </div>
        <div class="roadmap-item done">
          <div class="roadmap-status">완료</div>
          <h3>실시간 견적</h3>
          <p>자동 자재 계산, 비용 산출</p>
        </div>
        <div class="roadmap-item current">
          <div class="roadmap-status">진행 중</div>
          <h3>고급 내보내기</h3>
          <p>PDF 도면, 견적서 생성, 고해상도 렌더링</p>
        </div>
        <div class="roadmap-item upcoming">
          <div class="roadmap-status">예정</div>
          <h3>AR 미리보기</h3>
          <p>실제 공간에서 데크를 AR로 확인</p>
        </div>
        <div class="roadmap-item upcoming">
          <div class="roadmap-status">예정</div>
          <h3>시공업체 연결</h3>
          <p>설계한 데크를 시공할 업체 매칭</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="cta-section">
      <h2>지금 바로 시작하세요</h2>
      <p>무료로 데크 설계를 체험해 보세요</p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <CTA text="무료로 시작하기" link="/app" variant="primary" />
        <CTA text="문의하기" link="/contact" variant="secondary" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    position: relative;
    height: 400px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-accent) 0%, var(--color-accent-light) 100%);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .about-hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><defs><pattern id="grid" width="10" height="10" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"><path d="M 10 0 L 0 0 0 10" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)" stroke-width="0.5"/></pattern></defs><rect width="100" height="100" fill="url(%23grid)"/></svg>');
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .about-hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    text-align: center;
    color: white;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    opacity: 0.9;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-hero-content h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: white;
  }

  .about-hero-content p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .about-container {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  section h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .section-desc {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  /* 비전/미션 섹션 */
  .vision-section {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .vision-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .vision-label {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.25rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .vision-item h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .vision-text {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .value-card {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .value-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  .value-icon {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-accent) 0%, var(--color-accent-light) 100%);
    border-radius: 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: white;
    margin: 0 auto 1rem;
  }

  .value-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .value-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* 스토리 섹션 */
  .story-section {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    margin-left: -1.5rem;
    margin-right: -1.5rem;
    padding: 4rem 3rem;
  }

  .story-content {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .story-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .story-content p {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .story-content p:nth-child(3) {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* 통계 섹션 */
  .stats-section {
    padding: 0;
  }

  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-accent) 0%, var(--color-accent-light) 100%);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
  }

  .stat-item {
    text-align: center;
    color: white;
  }

  .stat-number {
    display: block;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 1rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  /* 타겟 사용자 */
  .users-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .user-card {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .user-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  .user-icon {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border-radius: 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin: 0 auto 1rem;
  }

  .user-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .user-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  /* 로드맵 */
  .roadmap {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .roadmap-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
    border-radius: 12px;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .roadmap-item.done {
    border-left: 4px solid #10B981;
  }

  .roadmap-item.current {
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent);
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
  }

  .roadmap-item.upcoming {
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gray-300);
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .roadmap-status {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .roadmap-item.done .roadmap-status {
    background: #D1FAE5;
    color: #065F46;
  }

  .roadmap-item.current .roadmap-status {
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: white;
  }

  .roadmap-item.upcoming .roadmap-status {
    background: var(--color-gray-200);
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }

  .roadmap-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .roadmap-item p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-accent) 0%, var(--color-accent-light) 100%);
    border-radius: 20px;
    color: white;
  }

  .cta-section h2 {
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .cta-section p {
    opacity: 0.9;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  /* Dark mode */
  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .value-card,
  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .user-card,
  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .roadmap-item {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .story-section {
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .user-icon {
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .roadmap-item.current {
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  /* 반응형 */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-hero-content h1 {
      font-size: 2.25rem;
    }

    .values-grid,
    .users-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .stats-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .about-hero {
      height: 320px;
    }

    .about-hero-content h1 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    .about-container {
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    .story-section {
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
      margin-left: -1rem;
      margin-right: -1rem;
    }

    .story-content p:nth-child(3) {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .roadmap-item {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
  }
</style>
